reviewText: I recently got this set, and I dont think the reviewers are being quite fair here, you have to know what your getting with this set. they are independent horrer movies and yes alot of them are really bad, but I quite enjoyed alot of them as well, some interesting stories and memerable movies, these are not blockbusters and have no stars in them the sound and picture quality arent good in alot of them but to get 100 movies for (...) I feel like if Ive enjoyed a handfull of them Ive gotten my monies worth. These titles are all on imbd and many of them have trailers on utube, I recomend looking at the trailers like bloodsucking babes from burbank and see what your getting, if your not a fan of drive-in or trashy type movies steer clear of this set, but I am enjoying it, if a movie is really bad I move on to the next one.This set is a combo of the Decrepit Crypt of Nightmares and the Tomb of Terrors 50 Movie Packs
